Interface Scheduler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SyncScheduler

    public interface Scheduler
    This is the interface for a scheduler which executes tasks for loading GVRf resources.

        Schedule a load request with a callback.
        Parameters:
        gvrContext - The GVRf Context object.
        outClass - The class object of a resource to be loaded.
        callback - A callback object to be notified when loading is done or failed.
